description: If you've spent the day canvassing and just need to take a breather, here are three games that have hit the spot recently for our pop culture critic.
title: 3 video games to take your mind off the election

description: "Leaders are not born," Granny says. "They're made through molding and modeling." That's why she and her granddaughter and putting on their hats and coats and walking to the polls.
title: Granny is going on 'The Walk' to the polls — and the whole town is invited
